    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Firmamus nos domnus <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/303" key="#Princeps">Arigis</persName> summus <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> genti Langubardorum,<rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3642" key="#Intercessory #Abbots">Arnoaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> nostro, absolutionem <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3410" key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ęcclesię</rs> Beate Sanctei Dei genitricis Marie et Sancti
                            Marciani</orgName> quem quoddam <persName ref="#people/3643"
                            key="#Abbots">Garoin</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> a novo fundamine ędificare visus fuet in locus
                        qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/112" key="#Villages/settlements">ad
                            Pletta</placeName>, secundum qualiter per suum <rs
                            key="#Episcopal_diploma">membranum firmitatis absolutionis</rs> quas
                            <persName ref="#people/3645" key="#Bishops">Iohannis</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> sancte sedis Ecclesię nostre
                        Beneventane predicti Garohin a suo anulo segillato emisit, nostra quidem
                        gloriosa potestas iuxta membranum ipsius Iohannis ępiscopi in predicte
                        sancte ęcclesię hunc nostrum absolutionem preceptus firmavimus, in eam
                        rationem ut tantummodo ad sacro nostro palatio audientiam habere debeas
                        sicut et ceteros nostra monasteria, in nostra sit potestatem ordinandi ipse
                        nostra ęcclesia qualiter nostra exemietas placuerit, et nullus episcopus
                        huius sancte sedis ęcclesię nostrę Beneventane vel ab eius sacerdotibus
                        nunquam requiratur in suo iure dominio, nec a nullus ex nostris gastaldeis
                        aut actionariis vel quisquam homo contra ea que nostra firmabet potestas,
                        sed perhenniter in suo arbitrio libertatis qualiter nostre clementie
                        placuerit vel a nostris successoribus ipse sacerdos qui ibidem ordinatus
                        fuerit libero nomine vivere valeat. Quod vero preceptus firmitatis
                        absolutionis ex iussus nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3644" key="#Notary">Ermerissus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Acto <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> mense aprili per indictione septima. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
